          "description": "Still waiting on medications since February 15! \ud83d\ude21After doctor visits and lab tests for PrEP, which was promised in 2-3 days, it is nowhere in sight. This seems to be a common issue in healthcare. Many messages, calls, I tried everything.\n\nI do not recommend this. Guys, find a better provider. Do not waste your time or your health!",
