          "user_photo_count": 2,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDLLu2ZpBPVhvkhUKAkn_fu6QtdVZk3X_8PnxDY4DB-fjbX3oSAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "My experience with MISTR has been nothing short of amazing. From getting the test kit to getting my prescriptions, it was so quick and easy. They provide detailed instructions for the at-home test kit, and my prescriptions show up very fast every month. They also have quick customer service. I couldn\u2019t recommend them enough if you\u2019re looking to get on (free) PrEP. It\u2019s definitely one of the best decisions I\u2019ve made in a while!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SdVZUWm1Wek52Um1SMVVYWnJiblEyUjJGRGFXYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xc55e5184274e5f25!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmRuVTZmVzNvRmR1UXZrbnQ2R2FDaWc%7C%7C?hl=en",
