          "description": "A+ overall rating... From ordering at home labs, chatting with the pharmacy, viewing results and/or medication, to video calls with your doctor, and renewing prescriptions, the process is streamlined to make it easy, fast, and convenient. Lightning fast shipping speeds and superb customer service relations. Would highly recommend.",
